  "body": "Network classes can be started and stopped. This pattern is \"forced\" on us because of libp2p, but we don't needed.\r\n\r\nThis forces Lodestar to mantain multiple AbortControllers, since you need a new one for each start. However if we change the flow to only be startable once a single AbortController can be passed as constructor parameter, and throw on start if it's already aborted.",
